# =====================================================================
# MONOREPO PROYECTO_MN — solo versionamos los MÓDULOS nuevos + motor.
# Los proyectos legacy (FUSION, OPEN, visor_dicom) y los datos quedan FUERA.
# Estrategia: ignorar TODO por defecto y "des-ignorar" (!) lo que sí va.
# =====================================================================

# --- Ignorar todo por defecto ---
/*

# --- Permitir la raíz del monorepo ---
!.gitignore
!README.md

# --- Módulos que SÍ versionamos (agregar aquí cada nuevo módulo) ---
!mod_SINCRO/
# !motor_principal/          # descomentar cuando exista
# !mod_XXX/                  # otros módulos futuros

# --- Legacy / no versionados explícitos ---
/- COL/

# =====================================================================
# Reglas internas (aplican dentro de los módulos versionados)
# =====================================================================

# --- Datos médicos (NUNCA versionar) ---
*.dcm
*.DCM
*.ima
*.IMA
*.dicom
data_test/
data_import/

# --- Salidas ---
output/
*.pdf
*.xlsx
*.csv

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# --- Entornos virtuales ---
.venv/
venv/
env/

# --- IDE / SO ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# --- Logs ---
*.log
*.tmp
